1
00:00:49,184 --> 00:00:52,768
=In Love With Loving You=
(Based on Love by Erxi on Qimao)

2
00:00:52,768 --> 00:00:55,520
=Episode 15=

3
00:01:00,520 --> 00:01:01,159
Kneel!

4
00:01:09,888 --> 00:01:11,136
(Song Zhaoli (Mr. Song))

5
00:01:13,760 --> 00:01:14,560
Hello, Mr. Song.

6
00:01:14,959 --> 00:01:20,560
You actually publicly criticized Xie Yao
at the meeting for Ji Xuan's sake?

7
00:01:21,200 --> 00:01:22,680
It seems you also know

8
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:25,760
that only Xie Yao did the stupid thing.

9
00:01:25,760 --> 00:01:27,359
I know

10
00:01:27,359 --> 00:01:29,200
what you are up to.

11
00:01:29,239 --> 00:01:32,719
You think you're already strong enough
to break free from the Song family

12
00:01:34,079 --> 00:01:36,120
and my control over you?

13
00:01:39,480 --> 00:01:42,680
You overestimate yourself.

14
00:01:42,799 --> 00:01:44,879
Do you really think you can do it?

15
00:01:46,280 --> 00:01:49,879
Today, I ask you one more time.

16
00:01:55,480 --> 00:01:59,120
Are you going to marry Xie Yao

17
00:02:00,120 --> 00:02:02,280
or not?

18
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:05,319
No.

19
00:02:05,680 --> 00:02:06,920
How dare you!

20
00:02:09,680 --> 00:02:12,039
(The chairman actually
slapped Song Zhaoli?)

21
00:02:19,960 --> 00:02:21,759
In the kidnapping case,

22
00:02:22,520 --> 00:02:28,439
you should be the one to die.

23
00:02:31,560 --> 00:02:32,439
Are you done?

24
00:02:33,280 --> 00:02:35,240
If there's nothing else, I'm leaving.

25
00:02:37,088 --> 00:02:37,599
Get out!

26
00:02:37,960 --> 00:02:39,879
Get out of here!

27
00:02:43,104 --> 00:02:43,680
Mr. Song?

28
00:02:45,360 --> 00:02:46,639
Mr. Song, can you hear me?

29
00:02:49,920 --> 00:02:50,592
Hello?

30
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:53,520
Are you calling me for something?

31
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:55,159
I called you?

32
00:02:56,319 --> 00:02:57,000
When?

33
00:02:57,680 --> 00:02:58,208
Just now.

34
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:02,039
I might have accidentally called you.

35
00:03:08,199 --> 00:03:09,080
Do you have any food?

36
00:03:09,759 --> 00:03:11,479
I haven't eaten yet. I'm hungry.

37
00:03:17,639 --> 00:03:18,599
Won't you have some too?

38
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:20,240
I've already eaten.

39
00:03:21,536 --> 00:03:22,360
Oh, I forgot.

40
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:25,479
Qiu Lin told me
you already ate with your boyfriend.

41
00:03:38,599 --> 00:03:39,680
Won't you drink with me?

42
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:42,560
Mr. Song, I've quit drinking.

43
00:03:54,752 --> 00:03:55,392
Because of me?

44
00:03:57,319 --> 00:03:58,280
Not really.

45
00:04:01,560 --> 00:04:02,360
Does it still hurt?

46
00:04:10,800 --> 00:04:13,719
I heard you got slapped over the phone.

47
00:04:16,639 --> 00:04:17,680
For refusing marriage?

48
00:04:19,439 --> 00:04:20,224
Yes.

49
00:04:21,879 --> 00:04:22,759
Then what will you do?

50
00:04:25,000 --> 00:04:26,000
There are other ways.

51
00:04:26,399 --> 00:04:27,120
What ways?

52
00:04:27,879 --> 00:04:30,199
Find a woman I can marry.

53
00:04:40,839 --> 00:04:41,480
Ji Xuan.

54
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:44,959
Do you know any suitable women?

55
00:04:46,439 --> 00:04:47,040
No.

56
00:04:49,160 --> 00:04:49,839
What about you?

57
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:55,959
Mr. Song, I have a boyfriend.

58
00:04:56,360 --> 00:04:57,600
You know that.

59
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:22,199
(Call me.)

60
00:05:22,399 --> 00:05:23,079
(Why?)

61
00:05:27,240 --> 00:05:28,319
(Just do what I say.)

62
00:05:28,319 --> 00:05:29,120
(Come on.)

63
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:37,079
Hey, Liao.

64
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:38,959
What's wrong with you?

65
00:05:39,439 --> 00:05:41,839
I argued with my grandpa
and got kicked out.

66
00:05:42,399 --> 00:05:43,959
Are you doing stand-up?

67
00:05:44,079 --> 00:05:47,160
Liao, could you lend me some money?

68
00:05:47,839 --> 00:05:48,839
I have nowhere to stay.

69
00:05:49,079 --> 00:05:51,199
You're now at Ji Xuan's place, right?

70
00:05:54,680 --> 00:05:56,000
Forget it if you can't.

71
00:05:56,639 --> 00:06:00,040
After all, the Liao
and Song families are long-time allies.

72
00:06:00,399 --> 00:06:02,079
It might put you
in a difficult position.

73
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:04,040
Impressive, Song.

74
00:06:04,439 --> 00:06:07,040
Seeing your situation,
I've learned one thing.

75
00:06:07,040 --> 00:06:09,920
The world is simple,
while the people are complicated.

76
00:06:10,519 --> 00:06:11,232
Alright.

77
00:06:11,800 --> 00:06:12,680
That's it.

78
00:06:22,519 --> 00:06:23,168
Cold compress.

79
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:34,120
Ji Xuan.

80
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:36,800
You heard everything just now.

81
00:06:36,959 --> 00:06:38,519
I'm homeless now.

82
00:06:39,079 --> 00:06:41,759
So could you please let me stay here?

83
00:07:11,886 --> 00:07:14,816
(Repay the Debt)

84
00:07:21,319 --> 00:07:21,959
Song Zhaoli.

85
00:07:28,480 --> 00:07:29,040
Yes?

86
00:07:46,680 --> 00:07:47,399
Song Zhaoli.

87
00:07:47,839 --> 00:07:50,240
Six years ago, did you come to my house?

88
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:59,936
(Repay the Debt)

89
00:08:28,279 --> 00:08:30,600
Six years ago,
I hadn't taken over Song Group yet.

90
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:32,240
I was busy taking training courses.

91
00:08:32,559 --> 00:08:35,279
I was not free at all, feeling boxed in.

92
00:08:37,879 --> 00:08:38,440
Why?

93
00:08:39,639 --> 00:08:40,399
Nothing.

94
00:08:44,279 --> 00:08:47,639
Your back reminds me of someone else.

95
00:08:51,919 --> 00:08:53,799
Someone had their eye
on you six years ago?

96
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:57,559
Look, it's too dangerous.

97
00:08:58,360 --> 00:09:00,080
I must protect you closely.

98
00:09:02,559 --> 00:09:03,679
For safety's sake,

99
00:09:03,679 --> 00:09:06,080
tonight, we sleep in the same room.

100
00:09:06,919 --> 00:09:09,799
Song Zhaoli, you are
the most dangerous person in Qingcheng.

101
00:09:11,120 --> 00:09:13,000
I made the bed for you.
You may go upstairs.

102
00:09:13,039 --> 00:09:13,984
I'll sleep downstairs.

103
00:09:23,519 --> 00:09:24,039
Mom.

104
00:09:25,840 --> 00:09:27,080
Although the rescue was timely,

105
00:09:27,159 --> 00:09:28,679
her condition isn't optimistic.

106
00:09:29,279 --> 00:09:31,440
I recommend a kidney transplant
as soon as possible.

107
00:09:51,039 --> 00:09:53,399
Dr. Li, I've been actively
searching for a kidney donor.

108
00:09:53,600 --> 00:09:55,480
Please take good care of her.

109
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:57,159
Of course.

110
00:09:58,960 --> 00:09:59,520
By the way,

111
00:10:00,039 --> 00:10:01,279
do you keep my medical report?

112
00:10:01,639 --> 00:10:02,159
Yes, I do.

113
00:10:02,679 --> 00:10:05,720
Could you please check
if my kidney is a match?

114
00:10:05,720 --> 00:10:08,759
Mr. Song, if it is,
will you give your own kidney?

115
00:10:08,759 --> 00:10:10,208
You're the sole heir of your family.

116
00:10:10,399 --> 00:10:11,759
The chairman might not approve.

117
00:10:12,399 --> 00:10:14,360
I decide what happens to my own body.

118
00:10:14,840 --> 00:10:15,679
Just do as I say.

119
00:10:18,000 --> 00:10:18,519
Yes.

120
00:10:25,360 --> 00:10:25,879
Mr. Song.

121
00:10:27,080 --> 00:10:28,960
May I take one week off?

122
00:10:29,399 --> 00:10:30,200
Is one week enough?

123
00:10:30,559 --> 00:10:31,480
Time is not an issue.

124
00:10:32,759 --> 00:10:33,519
Thank you.

125
00:10:36,559 --> 00:10:37,799
Here are the keys to my place.

126
00:10:38,279 --> 00:10:40,639
If you have nowhere else to go,
you can stay at my place.

127
00:11:15,671 --> 00:11:17,463
♪In the vast sea of stars♪

128
00:11:17,623 --> 00:11:19,503
♪Flickering neon lights♪

129
00:11:19,703 --> 00:11:23,031
♪Longing spreads
throughout the universe♪

130
00:11:23,543 --> 00:11:25,815
♪Every star is♪

131
00:11:26,103 --> 00:11:29,975
♪My heartbeat for you♪

132
00:11:31,287 --> 00:11:33,111
♪Want to ride the evening breeze♪

133
00:11:33,271 --> 00:11:34,823
♪And land in your arms♪

134
00:11:35,223 --> 00:11:38,679
♪The starry sky is like your eyes♪

135
00:11:38,935 --> 00:11:41,495
♪In the blue sky♪

136
00:11:41,559 --> 00:11:45,687
♪Your smile still lingers♪

137
00:11:46,615 --> 00:11:50,263
♪You are the brightest light
in my regrets♪

138
00:11:50,519 --> 00:11:54,183
♪You are the painful greeting
in my despair♪

139
00:11:54,391 --> 00:11:57,303
♪Can't find a cure♪

140
00:11:57,303 --> 00:12:01,815
♪To love you after we've parted♪

141
00:12:02,007 --> 00:12:06,039
♪You are the time I most want to keep♪

142
00:12:06,039 --> 00:12:09,903
♪The future I strive toward
in the darkness♪

143
00:12:09,903 --> 00:12:11,703
♪Slowly getting closer to you♪

144
00:12:11,799 --> 00:12:16,951
♪How I wish
I could give you my sunshine♪

145
00:12:17,591 --> 00:12:21,303
♪You are the brightest light
in my regrets♪

146
00:12:21,495 --> 00:12:24,247
♪Can't find a cure♪

147
00:12:24,375 --> 00:12:29,015
♪To love you after we've parted♪

148
00:12:29,183 --> 00:12:32,951
♪You are the time I most want to keep♪

149
00:12:33,175 --> 00:12:36,759
♪The future I strive toward
in the darkness♪

150
00:12:36,983 --> 00:12:39,023
♪Slowly getting closer to you♪

151
00:12:39,023 --> 00:12:44,023
♪How I wish
I could give you my sunshine♪
